mean_cn: v. 解除国有化，私有化
mean_en: to sell a company or an industry so that it is no longer owned by the government
word_etyma: de去掉 + na出生的 + tion表行为 + al表形容词 + ize表动词→denationalize去国有化，私有化
sentence: The U.S. government has denationalized some of its financial institutions.
sentence_trans: 美国政府已经将一些金融机构解除国有化。
